Class MoveHistoryObject

java.lang.Object
  model.MoveHistoryObject

public class MoveHistoryObject
extends java.lang.Object

The MoveHistoryObject class is an immutable class. A MoveHistoryObject represents a move that was made at a certain time in an Antichess game. It consists of a Move, a Time, and a Team.

Specification Fields
  • isWhite : boolean //boolean representing if the team making the move was white
  • timeOccurred : int //int representing time, in milliseconds, that the move was made
  • m : Move //the move made
  • capturedPiece : Piece //the piece captured by the move, m
  • capturedSquare : Square //the square that the capturedPiece was located at
